## 📦 Installation & Development

```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/coinseer.git
cd coinseer
git checkout new-enhancements
# install dependencies
npm install or pip install -r requirements.txt
# run the bot locally
npm run dev or python bot.py
```

